com.interpss.dstab.mach

Interface MachineController

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, DynamicDevice, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IDynamicSimulation, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAnnotateController, AbstractChildAnnotateController, AbstractExciter, AbstractGovernor, AbstractStabilizer, AnnotateExciter, AnnotateGovernor, AnnotateStabilizer, MachineControllerImpl

    public interface MachineController
extends DynamicDevice
    A representation of the model object 'Controller'. Generic machine controller class. Actual excitor, governor or pss model implementation will inheriate this base class.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type
    • Category
    • Machine
    See Also:
    DstabMachPackage.getMachineController()
